textTranslated: This restaurant is located in the center of Villafranca de los Caballeros, very close to Plaza de Espa√±a. It's highly recommended for dinner, lunch, or a celebration, as they also have a fairly large dining room. The atmosphere is still that of a typical restaurant, so nothing stands out in that regard. The menu includes pizzas, baguettes, hamburgers, sandwiches, portions, bombas, durum, and more elaborate mixed dishes. Prices range between ‚Ç¨5 and ‚Ç¨10 and are homemade and made with quality ingredients, as we have seen.
